we will create two pods exanmmple: 
node1 
192.168.0.20
wordpress

node2 
192.168.0.21
db 
  labels:
    app:mydb

these two pods above will be communicating through ClusterIP service 

## this service will be used as the hostname while connecting to the database
apiVersion:v1
metadata:
  name: mydb
spec:
  type: ClusterIP
  ports:
  - port: 3306
  selector:
    app: mydb
